OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FIncome tax to be cut by 1p 
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Ffrom April                 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, The basic rate of income tax will fall 
OL,6, from 20p to 19p in the pound from April
OL,7, next year, the chancellor has said.    
OL,9,FKwasi Kwarteng said the cut in the tax 
OL,10,Fpeople pay on earnings to 19% would    
OL,11,Fbenefit more than 31 million people.   
OL,13,FThe cut in the basic rate of income    
OL,14,Ftax, which applies to people that earn 
OL,15,Fbetween #12,571 to #50,270, comes a    
OL,16,Fyear earlier than planned.             
OL,18,FIn a surprise move, the UK's 45%       
OL,19,Fhighest tax band for people who earn   
OL,20,Fover #150,000 a year has been axed.    
